channel.title: MyRsWorldScape v1
channel.description:
[u][b]MyRsWorldScape v1[/b][/u] [u] Credits:[/u] Mod Allstar - 50% Tuts - 30% Me - 20% I gave smaller credits to myself because I didn't want to be flamed saying I didn't do that much (which I probably didn't) but it took me weeks to do this as I'm new to coding...[img]http://[/img]
What I added: New Custom Skills New Custom Train New Custom Pkbox New Starting gear Max money is 2147M Slayer Npc's give xp (when killed) ::Yell only after ::Starter (Stops spammers) ::huym2 (Your desired rights) So you don't have to log out then in to give yourself hidden owner or owner! ::hump ::afk New food shop (with all food) New pk shop (custom by me with new items) Prayer altars work Old pkbox is a fun pk (You don't lose item's) All skills work Skills are now 3x longer to 99 New veng emote and saying ::givehmod ::givehadmin Added the following, ::modglow, ::modglowoff, ::adminglow, ::adminglowoff, ::ownerglow, ::ownerglowoff, ::darkglow, ::darkglowoff, ::adminlook, ::ownerlook, ::noob (gives you all level 1 stats), ::runes, and ::brunes Changed the amount of money used on well (mod allstar's idea I just edited) Woodcut gives logs Fm gives ashes Herblore gives all herbs (random amounts up to 10) Crafting gives an onyx Rc gives water runes All skills that had given money now give 200k instead edited item bonuses/prices Deleted some shops Wyverns drop a ring of stone (1 in 40 chance) ((100+ str bonus)) Added a clan chat (It's bugged though) Added a jail with commands for mod+: ::jail (username) ::unjail (username) co-owners can't give staff you have to enter your own name Economy is great Removed jad from ::kqueen Added Saradomin sword and rune c'bow and rune throwing darts to the game with bonuses Removed a lot of global objects (& added some)

item.title: MyRsWorldScape v1
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

[quote=“killerj012, post:1, topic:279301”]MyRsWorldScape v1

Credits:

Mod Allstar - 50%
Tuts - 30%
Me - 20%

I gave smaller credits to myself because I didn’t want to be flamed saying I didn’t do that much (which I probably didn’t) but it took me weeks to do this as I’m new to coding…

What I added:

New Custom Skills
New Custom Train
New Custom Pkbox
New Starting gear
Max money is 2147M
Slayer Npc’s give xp (when killed)
::Yell only after ::Starter (Stops spammers)
::huym2 (Your desired rights) So you don’t have to log out then in to give yourself hidden owner or owner!
::hump
::afk
New food shop (with all food)
New pk shop (custom by me with new items)
Prayer altars work
Old pkbox is a fun pk (You don’t lose item’s)
All skills work
Skills are now 3x longer to 99
New veng emote and saying
::givehmod
::givehadmin
Added the following, ::modglow, ::modglowoff, ::adminglow, ::adminglowoff, ::ownerglow, ::ownerglowoff, ::darkglow, ::darkglowoff, ::adminlook, ::ownerlook, ::noob (gives you all level 1 stats), ::runes, and ::brunes
Changed the amount of money used on well (mod allstar’s idea I just edited)
Woodcut gives logs
Fm gives ashes
Herblore gives all herbs (random amounts up to 10)
Crafting gives an onyx
Rc gives water runes
All skills that had given money now give 200k instead
edited item bonuses/prices
Deleted some shops
Wyverns drop a ring of stone (1 in 40 chance) ((100+ str bonus))
Added a clan chat (It’s bugged though)
Added a jail with commands for mod+: ::jail (username) ::unjail (username)
co-owners can’t give staff you have to enter your own name
Economy is great
Removed jad from ::kqueen
Added Saradomin sword and rune c’bow and rune throwing darts to the game with bonuses
Removed a lot of global objects (& added some)

PICTURES:

ModGlow Thanks to the Tuts

Adminglow Thanks to the Tuts

Ownerglow Thanks to the Tuts

Darkglow Thanks to the Tuts

Custom Admin Look (May be similar to other sources but not leeched thought of by “luke” on my server)

Custom Owner Look (Yes again it may look leeched but it’s not thought of by yours truly)

Prayer Altars do work (Thanks to the Tuts)

Custom Pkbox Shop (Changed everything)

Custom Pkbox (Not leeched [No Tuts used]) [Mod/Admin Weps don’t work in wilderness zones]

New Starting Place (With talking npc’s you can edit)

Brand New Veng (Not Leeched [No Tuts used])

New Train With New Npc’s and Drops (Cash drops thanks to a tutorial [Item drops no] {DID NOT CHANGE KBD DROPS})

Woodcutting gives logs, crafting gives an onyx, Firemaking gives ashes, herblore gives potions, mining gives 200k, thieving (same as All-Star scape except different amounts), farming same, runecrafting runes, smithing same, agility 200k

Only took a pic of wc though

This is the main picture of the skills place (not leeched [No Tuts used])

::Yell only after ::Starter (Stop people from spamming)

::huym2 (Your desired Rights) [This was added by a friend of mine Idk if it’s copied or leeched]

My Custom Food Shop (No more rays!)

Added an Afk Command (No tuts used figured out while changing vengeance also haven’t added a ::back command)

[size=10pt]You can download it here:[/size]

MyRsWorldScape v1 Download![/font]

Sorry for the inconvenience

http://s726.photobucket.com/albums/ww262/killerj012/MyRsWorldScape%20v1/

[size=10pt][size=10pt]Please TELL ME what you would like to SEE IN v2? ILL TRY MY BEST :)[/size][/size][/quote]
